1) Set Up Email-Sending Functionality
   Use Python's smtplib to send phishing emails.
    Install necessary libraries:
    pip3 install email
2) Write the Email Generator Script
    Save the following script as phishing_email.py
3) Replace:
    your_email@example.com and your_password with your email credentials.
    http://your_ngrok_url_here with the URL of your fake login page.
4) Test Sending Emails
    Run the script:
    python3 phishing_email.py
5) Avoid Spam Filters
   Use legitimate-sounding subject lines.
   Change email content regularly to avoid detection.
